Remove redundant GO terms

remove_redundant_go.Rd

Given the output of get_enriched_go or goseq, remove redundant GO terms.

Usage

remove_redundant_go(
  obj,
  go_category_col = "category",
  p_value_col = "over_represented_pvalue"
)

Arguments

obj

data.frame containing goseq results as generated by

`go_category_col`

character column name for GO terms

`p_value_col`

character column name for p-values get_enriched_go or goseq.

Value

Returns obj with redundant GO terms filtered out.
